==English==
===Noun===
'''Seine'''

#''(proper noun)'' {{rivers}} A [[river]] of northern [[France]] that flows through [[Paris]] for about 772 km (480 mi) to the [[English Channel]] near [[Le Havre]].
#''(proper noun)'' A [[department]] in [[France]], the capital city of which is [[Paris]].

